Players who want to make the best of the game need to know the best way to approach it. There’s power-up’s, new characters and several missions you’ll need to master as you run through the subways. In this game you are really will have lack of coins. But with this cheat code youll get unlimited coins. So you can buy any upgrades and make much higher score!

And here you can find unlimited keys! When creators entered keys to the game, it has become much more interesting and easier, because after you bumped into something you are given a chance to continue. Unfortunately, this chance is given only if you have special keys. Usually, all the players are suffering from a lack of keys, but not you ... This code gives you an unlimited supply of keys that you can use to continue after losing. This allows you to set the record for the biggest of your life!

And if you want to have any board, just use this...You can change you character and board by clicking on ME icon. There will be several characters available and you can choose one of them by buying it. Purchasing character and board improve your performance while playing game. Default character will run very fast and you cant control it after reaching long distance. Selecting new character will go slowly for long distance and this will improve the chance for collecting more coins.

There are two special boards available one is Bouncer and the other is Lowrider. Bouncer board will help you to jump above the train as you do while using Super Sneakers. While using Lowrider board it automatically crouch below the rail blocks. Using other ordinary boards you need to crouch manually for every rail blocks. Only this two board has got special powers.
